text: George Campbell (born June 22, 2001) is an American soccer player who plays for Atlanta United in MLS. == Club career == Campbell appeared for USL Championship side Atlanta United 2 after appearing for Atlanta United's academy team since 2016.https://www.atlutd.com/academy/u-17 On July 9, 2019, Campbell signed as a Homegrown Player for Atlanta United, effective on January 1, 2020. == References == == External links == * * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:American soccer players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Atlanta United 2 players Category:Atlanta United FC players Category:Soccer players from Georgia (U.S. state) Category:Sportspeople from Atlanta Category:USL Championship players Category:Major League Soccer players Category:Homegrown Players (MLS)
